{"tid":2143283,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★HK No IT 正式啟動！","createTime":"2020-08-07T04:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T06:16:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"299252e05ae8435738432c5fb80166b60bc27858","tid":2143283,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc81e3eb9cbd99e653a203b4f53579afd906f0ca","tid":2143283,"uid":12628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:11:34.000Z","msg":"<code>\n系統已啟動N世\n</code>"},{"pid":"eb854911b908c89acc05ed23153469e5616d16f3","tid":2143283,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:12:27.000Z","msg":"香港科技界憂美針對中國推「清潔網絡政策」 或重本港創科業<br />\n<br />\n香港科技界指，本港不少初創企業及創科業，都有中方甚至是美方的資金，本來是全球化下的優勢，現時變為中美角力下的「負累」。  香港資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑表示：「中美貿易戰中間都是打『科技戰』，我們經常說現在其實已經不是『冷戰』，已經去到『暖戰』，甚至乎很接近一個『熱戰』的階段。如果現在要做科技要想去國際市場，要想多一點政治上的元素，或資金上、資金鏈究竟是不同國家成份，要想你想去那些地方，做甚麼生意。」  他舉例美國的太平洋海底電纜，本來直接由洛杉磯連接香港，之後美方決定改駁到台灣。方保僑擔心，美國盟友會有其他跟進措施，香港可能會被邊緣化。  方保僑指：「很多科技公司、數據中心都會跟隨光纖走，因為光纖其實是數據的通道，加強互聯網的速度，如果這些光纖離開(香港)，可能很多公司會考慮會否來港做亞太中心，甚至乎興建數據中心都會有影響。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5f2cbd5d34b031611628f579/香港科技界憂美針對中國推清潔網絡政策-或重本港創科業\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5f2cbd5d34b031611628f579%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E7%95%8C%E6%86%82%E7%BE%8E%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8E%A8%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96-%E6%88%96%E9%87%8D%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E5%89%B5%E7%A7%91%E6%A5%AD&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=aa3a2ea5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5f2cbd5d34b031611628f579/香港科技界憂美針對中國推清潔網絡政策-或重本港創科業</a>"},{"pid":"5e9632797a4568391c9ca5710ae9a224b29fcfd3","tid":2143283,"uid":168930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:18:21.000Z","msg":"又唔夠錢洗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6494075fdbbfd19d5ff65d5ee9afd9f97557cfb","tid":2143283,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:22:24.000Z","msg":"搵楊局長落去問下教主有咩方法拆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcdb1f682e975ffdf37d2706c3428fdba6ad4ec","tid":2143283,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6494075fdbbfd19d5ff65d5ee9afd9f97557cfb","tid":2143283,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:22:24.000Z","msg":"搵楊局長落去問下教主有咩方法拆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181129/s00001/abf9e302b3b8583a4e8a60a35ca20cbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181129%2Fs00001%2Fabf9e302b3b8583a4e8a60a35ca20cbc.jpg&h=7ee85828&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4141c94a53f53d1508033800c33422574576a78","tid":2143283,"uid":262616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6494075fdbbfd19d5ff65d5ee9afd9f97557cfb","tid":2143283,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:22:24.000Z","msg":"搵楊局長落去問下教主有咩方法拆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:29:52.000Z","msg":"乜唔係薜局長咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f21beabd4ff0771add1787b3cd21f0edb110c3a","tid":2143283,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T04:30:43.000Z","msg":"基本法腐乳"},{"pid":"1a1b598b3d24e5d30345f3216ca8f10e7ea955a0","tid":2143283,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":